  <section class="about">
    <h1>About BioTrac</h1>
    <p>BioTrac is a social enterprise committed to transforming lives through education in health and financial literacy. We believe that informed individuals build resilient families and communities.</p>

    <h2>Our Vision</h2>
    <p>A world where every person — regardless of age or background — can access the knowledge they need to live healthy and financially stable lives.</p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>To deliver relevant, practical, and culturally responsive training programs in schools, communities, and corporate environments.</p>

    <h2>Our Team</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Mugisha David</strong> – Founder & Lead Educator</li>
      <li><strong>Mpoza Joseph</strong> – Programs Director</li>
      <li><strong>Kajimu Jhon</strong> – Outreach Lead</li>
      <li><strong>Paul</strong> – Monitoring & Partnerships</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

